take him down right now would be suicidal.

308
00:18:28,078 --> 00:18:29,330
I'm not going to do it.

309
00:18:29,483 --> 00:18:32,900
It would be like a bug walking
into a spider's web on purpose.

310
00:18:33,253 --> 00:18:34,294
Hah! Come on.

311
00:18:35,927 --> 00:18:39,673
